<p><strong>NAME OF TALE</strong> Chiaroscuro<br />
<strong>Author:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tufto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3337265); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3337265&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721413" alt="Tufto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3337265)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tufto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3337265); return false;">Tufto</a></span>. This tale is part of the <a href="/the-man-who-wasnt-there-hub">Man Who Wasn't There</a> canon, and is the second entry for Team Nobody's Winning in the <a href="/canon-renaissance-contest">Canon Renaissance Contest</a>. More of Tufto's work can be found <a href="/tufto-personnel-file">here</a>.<br />
<strong>Images:</strong> The first image is a modified version of <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Plymouth_City_Noir.jpg">this CC0 photograph</a>.<br />
The second image is a modified version of <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Wake_Up_Moon_(29339717).jpeg">this CC-BY 3.0 photo</a>.</p>
